<i>Was born and raised</i>

376
00:24:02,190 --> 00:24:04,890
<i>The place where he</i>

377
00:24:05,190 --> 00:24:08,390
<i>Was born and raised</i>

378
00:24:08,590 --> 00:24:12,790
<i>For six long years</i>

