00:24:13,090 --> 00:24:15,490
<i>I've been in trouble</i>

380
00:24:15,790 --> 00:24:18,290
<i>No pleasure here</i>

381
00:24:18,590 --> 00:24:21,790
<i>On Earth I found</i>

382
00:24:21,990 --> 00:24:26,090
<i>For in this world</i>

383
00:24:26,290 --> 00:24:28,390
<i>I'm bound to ramble</i>

384
00:24:28,590 --> 00:24:31,490
<i>I have no friends</i>

385
00:24:31,690 --> 00:24:34,190
<i>To help me now</i>

386
00:24:34,490 --> 00:24:36,890
<i>He has no friends</i>

387
00:24:37,190 --> 00:24:40,490
<i>To help him now</i>

388
00:24:40,790 --> 00:24:44,990
<i>Maybe your friends think</i>

389
00:24:45,290 --> 00:24:47,690
<i>I'm just a stranger</i>

